<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Password Updated Successfully</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .alert {
      padding: 12px 20px;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      border-left: 4px solid #0070f3;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Password Updated</h1>
  
  <div class="alert">
    <p>Your password was successfully updated on {{formatDate timestamp}}.</p>
  </div>
  
  <p>If you did not make this change, please contact our support team immediately as your account may have been compromised.</p>
  
  <p>For your security, we recommend:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Using unique passwords for each of your online accounts</li>
    <li>Enabling two-factor authentication when available</li>
    <li>Regularly reviewing your account activity</li>
  </ul>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>Best regards,<br>Gradiant Team</p>
    <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
  </div>
